value.0: The Qion Hive Broodmother is a grotesque, unholy abomination that appears to be an amalgamated collection of meat and body parts. Flesh and corpses that it had devoured come to be gruesomely drawn into its writhing mass, and then after being processed is thereafter spat out as larvaes and eggs which then hatch into its hungry spawns: the Qion Slugs. These slugs traverse the expanse of Hutlar, with those that survive drawn back to the broodmother's nest, only to be reabsorbed back. The Broodmother behaves with a malevolent intellect and cunning, and bits and pieces of limbs that jut forth from it snatch at and snare its victims who may seek to flee from it...
